{
  "text": "Can you give me the same type of information that we've been getting with working on now with respect to the self-relationship with war and rumors of war. I am Ra. You may see this in relationship to your gadgets. This war and self relationship is a fundamental perception of the maturing entity. There is a great chance to accelerate in whatever direction is desired. One may polarize negatively by assuming abelicose attitudes for whatever reason one may find oneself in the situation of war and polarize somewhat towards the positive, activating orange, yellow, and then green by heroic, if you may call them this, actions taken to preserve the mind, a body, a spirit complexes of other selves. Finally, one may polarize very strongly a third ray by expressing the principle of universal love at the total expense of any distortion towards involvement in abelico's actions. In this way, the entity may become a conscious being in a very brief span of your time space. This may be seen to be what you would call a traumatic progression. It is to be noted that among your entities a large percentage of all progression has as catalyst trauma.",
